spark.sql("select ABT_INMATE_ID,SEX,ADMTYPE,OFFGENERAL,ADMITYR,RELEASEYR,SENTLGTH,OFFDETAIL,RACE,AGEADMIT,TIMESRVD,RELTYPE,STATE from term_rec").createOrReplaceTempView("term_rec_clV1")
